Sentencas: Recently, powder injection molding (PIM) has been exploited in the field of solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs), especially for fabricating anode supports.
Titulo: Effect of pre-calcined ceramic powders at different temperatures on Ni-YSZ anode-supported SOFC cell/stack by low pressure injection molding

Sentencas: The current study employs low pressure injection molding (LPIM) to manufacture near net shape, porous, tubular NiO-yttria stabilized zirconia (YSZ) anode supports for anode supported SOFCs.
Titulo: Effect of pre-calcined ceramic powders at different temperatures on Ni-YSZ anode-supported SOFC cell/stack by low pressure injection molding

Sentencas: The study investigates the effects of pre-calcining temperature of the ceramic powder on the microstructure, porosity and electrochemical performance of the cells in detail.
Titulo: Effect of pre-calcined ceramic powders at different temperatures on Ni-YSZ anode-supported SOFC cell/stack by low pressure injection molding

Sentencas: Archimedes tests reveal that the porosity of an unreduced NiO-YSZ anode with 900 degrees C pre-calcined powder reaches a high of 25.9%, approaching the optimal value of 26%.
Titulo: Effect of pre-calcined ceramic powders at different temperatures on Ni-YSZ anode-supported SOFC cell/stack by low pressure injection molding

Sentencas: Meanwhile, the anode prepared under this condition possesses more porous and homogeneous microstructures.
Titulo: Effect of pre-calcined ceramic powders at different temperatures on Ni-YSZ anode-supported SOFC cell/stack by low pressure injection molding

Sentencas: At 800 degrees C, with humidified hydrogen as fuel and ambient air as the oxidant, the single cell with 900 degrees C pre-calcined powder delivers a maximum power density of 671 mW cm(-2) while the cell with raw powder, 555 mW cm(-2), and the cell with 1000 degrees C pre-calcined powder, 648 mW cm(-2).
Titulo: Effect of pre-calcined ceramic powders at different temperatures on Ni-YSZ anode-supported SOFC cell/stack by low pressure injection molding

Sentencas: A four-cell stack is assembled by connecting four single cells in series.
Titulo: Effect of pre-calcined ceramic powders at different temperatures on Ni-YSZ anode-supported SOFC cell/stack by low pressure injection molding

Sentencas: The stack could provide a maximum output power of 4.6 W and an open circuit voltage of 3.2 V when fuelled with humidified hydrogen at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Effect of pre-calcined ceramic powders at different temperatures on Ni-YSZ anode-supported SOFC cell/stack by low pressure injection molding
